00:15:33,060 --> 00:15:35,860
No need to save money for me.

194
00:15:40,530 --> 00:15:42,810
Oh, your homeroom teacher is calling.

195
00:15:42,810 --> 00:15:46,360
Calling me at this time... Is it that he wants to discuss

196
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:48,330
