203
00:16:27,740 --> 00:16:31,690
- You left everything else empty, is that right?
- Yes.

204
00:16:31,690 --> 00:16:34,850
Didn't I tell you that you're not allowed to apply for architecture?!

205
00:16:34,850 --> 00:16:36,790
Go! Fix it!

206
00:16:36,790 --> 00:16:39,730
- I won't fix it.
- Will you fix it?

207
00:16:40,460 --> 00:16:43,020
- No.
- You!

208
00:16:47,380 --> 00:16:51,000
I've told you long ago that I won't support you studying architecture.

209
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:55,820
