- You know to come back?
- Yeah.

257
00:26:17,070 --> 00:26:20,330
What are you "yeah-ing" for? You little brat.

258
00:26:20,330 --> 00:26:23,920
You only know to fight against me every day.

259
00:26:24,720 --> 00:26:26,580
Go inside and eat.

260
