290
00:31:33,080 --> 00:31:35,670
I'll b-buy you a new one.

291
00:31:35,670 --> 00:31:39,550
N-No need. I have a lot at home. I have a lot, it's fine.

292
00:31:39,550 --> 00:31:42,020
Here. Sorry about that.

293
00:31:43,980 --> 00:31:47,830
It's really fine, Senior. It's fine.

294
00:32:07,160 --> 00:32:08,690
You came?

295
00:32:08,690 --> 00:32:11,150
You're still working so hard even though the exam has ended.

296
00:32:11,150 --> 00:32:14,030
Uncle, I want to buy some paint.

297
00:32:14,030 --> 00:32:16,500
Do you have the entire set of Marie's (Brand name)?

298
00:32:16,500 --> 00:32:20,460
Marie's? You didn't use to use this brand.

299
00:32:21,050 --> 00:32:24,110
It's a gift for someone. I'm afraid she might not adjust well to a new brand.

300
00:32:24,110 --> 00:32:26,720
If it's a gift, then they must use the expensive one.

301
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:31,710
I just got a new batch and they're pretty good. Just... See there, that girl has been looking at them all day.

302
00:32:38,380 --> 00:32:40,110
Money.

303
00:32:40,110 --> 00:32:45,060
Can't my mom just give me a little bit more allowance?

304
00:32:49,390 --> 00:32:52,560
Uncle, give me a box of the brand that she's holding.

305
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:55,160
Okay, I'll go to the back and get it.

306
00:33:22,760 --> 00:33:25,690
She just had to make me take this exam.

307
00:33:25,690 --> 00:33:28,600
If I don't pass the fifth level, she won't let me study Fine Arts.

308
00:33:28,600 --> 00:33:33,380
She doesn't give me an allowance and doesn't even send me off to the exam.

309
00:33:33,380 --> 00:33:36,460
Mom really does have a heart of stone.

310
00:33:37,770 --> 00:33:39,560
Xia Miaomiao.

311
00:33:40,710 --> 00:33:42,830
Senior?

312
00:33:42,830 --> 00:33:46,600
Why... Why are you here?

313
00:33:48,910 --> 00:33:50,570
To repay a debt.

314
00:33:50,570 --> 00:33:52,350
I...

315
00:33:53,430 --> 00:33:56,080
No, no, no. No need.

316
00:33:56,080 --> 00:33:59,660
I have a lot of paint, and...

317
00:33:59,660 --> 00:34:03,550
and this one is too expensive. I can't accept it.

318
00:34:04,420 --> 00:34:07,790
I broke your paint tube so it's only right for me to give you a new one.

319
00:34:09,730 --> 00:34:11,070
N-No.

320
00:34:11,070 --> 00:34:14,030
I have a lot of boxes of this brand.

321
00:34:16,470 --> 00:34:18,480
Xia Miaomiao.

322
00:34:19,730 --> 00:34:22,340
You like this paint's brand, don't you?

323
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:30,060
Take it.

324
00:34:33,390 --> 00:34:35,800
Thank you, Senior.

325
00:34:38,280 --> 00:34:43,430
I will definitely work hard with these paints and get a good score.

326
00:34:43,430 --> 00:34:46,830
Okay. Then I'll wait for your good news.

327
00:34:47,550 --> 00:34:49,590
Hurry and go in. Fighting.

328
00:34:49,590 --> 00:34:51,020
Fighting!

329
00:35:42,010 --> 00:35:44,900
You think there's nothing I can do if you won't let me deliver?

330
00:37:09,890 --> 00:37:12,710
You locked my motorcycle again! Are you mental!

331
00:37:20,170 --> 00:37:23,820
Admissions Letter

332
00:37:23,820 --> 00:37:29,020
Haicheng University

333
00:37:38,870 --> 00:37:40,630
I obviously pushed the "Stop receiving orders" button,

334
00:37:40,630 --> 00:37:43,700
so why is the platform still giving me delivery orders so late at night?

