00:38:16,920 --> 00:38:20,790
Fine Arts Standardized Exam Certification - Pass Grade: 8

338
00:38:45,500 --> 00:38:48,890
Stop smiling. Hurry and help me with my homework.

339
00:38:48,890 --> 00:38:52,690
Don't you have one more week before school starts? Why are you in such a hurry?

340
00:38:52,690 --> 00:38:55,570
