00:39:29,630 --> 00:39:32,060
Teacher Liang.

351
00:39:32,060 --> 00:39:33,490
It's Xia Miaomiao.

352
00:39:33,490 --> 00:39:35,800
What's up that you are so happy?

353
00:39:37,850 --> 00:39:40,450
What level did you get? Let me see.

354
00:39:41,510 --> 00:39:44,400
- Level 8.
