355
00:39:46,660 --> 00:39:49,860
Not bad. Not bad, not bad.

356
00:39:50,570 --> 00:39:52,060
Under my guidance,

357
00:39:52,060 --> 00:39:56,030
Student Miaomiao has improved dramatically.

358
00:39:56,030 --> 00:39:59,620
But... you can't be arrogant. Continue to work hard, okay?

