00:40:09,970 --> 00:40:11,960
Oh, you're here?

363
00:40:14,990 --> 00:40:16,720
I'm here.

364
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:30,980
So you haven't seen Liang Younian all this time?

365
00:40:30,980 --> 00:40:35,500
Yeah, I thought I would see him in the art studio today.

366
00:40:35,500 --> 00:40:39,260
Don't you have his phone number? Just call him and invite him out.

